This modern architecturally designed tilt panel building features the following:

•	501sqm* Corporate grade office all on ground level
•	3,018sqm* Warehouse with minimum internal clearance of 8.75 metres
•	12,153sqm* Freehold Industrial land holding 
•	Over 5,000sqm* of heavy duty concrete hardstand
•	Warehouse access by four (4) electric container height roller doors with substantial awnings
•	Secured site with full drive around access and two (2) electric boom gates
•	The property is flood free (1974 & 2011)

*Approx.

The building has excellent access to Ipswich, Logan and Centenary Motorways and is located amongst international and well established companies, including Coca Cola, Target, Coles, Iron Mountain and Allied Pickfords.
                
The quality of this facility, including the large area of concreted hardstand and easy access to highway networks, make this one of the best industrial buildings of its size on Brisbane’s southside.

For further details or to arrange an inspection please don’t hesitate to contact CBRE the Marketing Agents.

This modern office and warehouse facility features the following:
+  858sqm* Corporate Office and showroom (split to suit)
+  2,650sqm* Functional warehouse area
+  Pallet racking included (subject to negotiation)
+  30KW Solar system 
+  ESFR Sprinkler system throughout
+  Large all-weather canter lever awning
+  Warehouse access by three on grade roller doors and 2 loading docks
+  Secured site with full drive around access
+  The property is flood free (1974 & 2011)
*Approx.

The is a modern distribution facility with quality office, high bay warehouse and drive around truck access. Constructed of dado panel with the office and showroom split over two levels and fitted to corporate specifications. The warehouse is accessed via 3 container height electric roller doors covered by large all weather awnings and there are two sunken loading docks with dock levellers for container unloading.

The property is situated in the tightly held suburb of Richlands, just 14 km from the Brisbane CBD. Strategically located to offer exceptional access to the major south west arterial road networks, Centenary Highway and the Ipswich Motorway ensuring occupiers highly efficient movement through Brisbane’s transport network. 

For further details or to arrange an inspection please don’t hesitate to contact CBRE the Exclusive Agents.

Located approx. 15km from Brisbane CBD, 2/145 Archerfield Road, Richlands is a 1,230sqm* warehouse/office. Offering fantastic access to all the Western Corridor’s major arterials, including directly to the Ipswich motorway. 


Key features include: 
•	1,230sqm* modern tilt-panel office/warehouse facility
•	1,080sqm* of clearspan warehouse with great internal height
•	150sqm* of corporate office space
•	4 x electric roller doors
•	Fully secured hardstand area
•	Available April 2022


For further information regarding this outstanding opportunity or should you wish to arrange an inspection, please contact Marketing Agent Sean Skeffington of CBRE today.
